text: The Five is an American conservative political talk show on Fox News Channel. It is hosted by Greg Gutfeld, Dana Perino, Jesse Watters, Jeanine Pirro, Jessica Tarlov and Harold Ford Jr. to talk about stories, political issues, and pop culture. The one-hour show premiered on July 11, 2011. It airs live weekdays at 5 p.m. ET, with repeat episodes airing at 5 a.m. ET and 5 p.m. ET on Saturdays. ==References== Category:2011 American television series debuts Category:Fox television series
